BestSoFar.framework.core.helper

Class VersionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • BestSoFar.framework.core.helper.VersionInfo
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    VersionInfoImpl

    public abstract class VersionInfo
extends Object
    Each EventuallyImmutable object has one VersionInfo object which describes tracks its earlier and later versions.

      • updateAllToLatest
